channel.title: Food issue?
channel.description:
i am using the project czar source and i have run across an issue and i dont know when or how it happend but for some reason i cannot eat unless i have a weapon in the weapon slot if i remove the weapon i cannot eat untill i put the weapon back on i have tested it multiple times with the same result and tried it with all other items on it will ONLY eat if i have a weapon attached to me
is there any way to fix this issue?
